Package ca.polymtl.inf3995.oronos.widgets.containers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractWidgetContainer<T extends ContainableWidget>
    Abstract Widget Container This abstract class is parent to any widget in need of a list (of CAN tags in most cases).
    DualWidget
    Dual Widget This Dual Widget class is responsible of displaying two views either vertically aligned or horizontally aligned.
    Rocket
    Rocket This class represent the rocket as a xml tag having a name and a rocket id and being parent of many views.
    Tab
    Tab This class represent a tab (container that is a child of a tabContainer and parent to an Oronos View).
    TabContainer
    Tab Container This class represent a Tab Container (child to any sort of container and parent to tab children).

    Enum of all possible orientations of a Dual Widget.
